memberdef.name: StoreData

briefdescription.para: Will store scienceData from a passed in list of IScienceDataContainer type. The List is first sorted in Order from highest sciencedata count to lowest. If excludeScienceContainers is true any ModuleScienceContainer's in the input list will be removed (default false). If scienceContainerPriority is false any ModuleScienceContainer's in the input list will be moved to the end of the list. (default false).

parameterdescription.para: List of passed in IScienceDataContainer type
If true repeat experiments found will be dumpled, if false they will be left where they are
Optional Parameter (default false) - If true will Exclude any ModuleScienceContainers from the list before moving the science data
Optional Paramater (default false) - If true will give ModuleScienceContainers priority
